

Device objects will emit lifecycle events

A persisence manager will persist object descriptor/data.

Dependency manager may store dependencies external to the objects
Will manager event listeners based on dependencies added or removed
Will manage lifecycle state of objects dependent on other objects 

MQTT transportwill coordinate events between devie objects and an MQTT server.

Configuration views will use object configuration descriptors to prompt users for configuration input. Will display current value (value updated on change event)
Will accept input and set configuration value.
Object will act on the configuration changes made.
